00:19:05.355 --> 00:19:08.415
The company faced severe financial losses.

00:19:08.985 --> 00:19:13.274
They decided to lay off a significant
portion of their workforce.

00:19:13.844 --> 00:19:17.804
Which of the following connectors
can be used to combine the above

00:19:17.804 --> 00:19:24.645
two sentences into one options
A, although B, in addition, C.

00:19:24.855 --> 00:19:31.125
Consequently D, despite understand the
question before moving to explanation.

00:19:32.010 --> 00:19:32.820
Solution.

00:19:33.030 --> 00:19:37.139
Step one, understand the
relationship between the sentences.

00:19:37.620 --> 00:19:41.939
Sentence one tells us the
company faced financial losses.

00:19:42.360 --> 00:19:45.960
Sentence two says they
decided to lay off employees.

00:19:46.200 --> 00:19:49.260
Now think why would
they lay off employees?

00:19:49.710 --> 00:19:54.389
It's a direct outcome, a result of
those financial losses, isn't it?

00:19:55.150 --> 00:19:59.620
So we are looking for a connector
that expresses cause and effect.

00:19:59.890 --> 00:20:03.910
It's like you don't study,
consequently, you don't pass.

00:20:04.360 --> 00:20:07.180
Step two, analyze the given options.

00:20:07.510 --> 00:20:12.820
A, although this one says even though
this happened, something else happened,

00:20:13.060 --> 00:20:15.640
it expresses contrast or concession.

00:20:15.880 --> 00:20:17.020
Not a good fit here.

00:20:17.439 --> 00:20:23.949
B. In addition, this just adds more
information like saying, I had samosas,

00:20:24.100 --> 00:20:27.760
in addition, I had jy not showing cause.

00:20:28.030 --> 00:20:30.550
C, consequently, aha.

00:20:30.790 --> 00:20:34.030
This word screams result or consequence.

00:20:34.210 --> 00:20:36.669
Exactly what we need for cause and effect.

00:20:36.939 --> 00:20:42.699
D, despite, again, this is for
contrast or concession, like although.

00:20:43.300 --> 00:20:47.590
Step three, choose the best
fit based on our analysis.

00:20:47.740 --> 00:20:50.650
Consequently is the most
appropriate connector.

00:20:51.010 --> 00:20:55.420
It clearly indicates that the layoffs
were a direct consequence of the

00:20:55.420 --> 00:20:58.180
financial losses combined sentence.

00:20:58.480 --> 00:21:01.120
The company faced severe financial losses.

00:21:01.435 --> 00:21:06.865
Consequently, they decided to lay off a
significant portion of their workforce.

00:21:07.195 --> 00:21:09.145
