00:21:09.534 --> 00:21:12.054
She studied diligently for the exam.

00:21:12.415 --> 00:21:14.965
She still found some
questions challenging.

00:21:15.445 --> 00:21:18.865
Which of the following connectors
can be used to combine the

00:21:18.865 --> 00:21:21.085
above two sentences into one?

00:21:21.400 --> 00:21:27.760
Options A, moreover B, however,
C, therefore D, because

00:21:28.090 --> 00:21:32.440
understand the question before
moving to explanation solution.

00:21:32.680 --> 00:21:38.200
Step one, understand the relationship
between the sentences sentence one

00:21:38.410 --> 00:21:40.445
tells us she studied very hard.

00:21:41.015 --> 00:21:44.795
Sentence two tells us that
despite studying hard, she

00:21:44.795 --> 00:21:46.565
still found things challenging.

00:21:46.775 --> 00:21:49.085
There's a clear contrast here, isn't it?

00:21:49.535 --> 00:21:54.665
It's like preparing for a sunny day, but
still getting drenched in a sudden shower.

00:21:54.995 --> 00:21:58.325
We need a connector that
expresses this contrast.

00:21:58.565 --> 00:22:01.295
Step two, analyze the given options.

00:22:01.565 --> 00:22:06.905
A. Moreover, this means in addition,
or furthermore, no contrast here.

00:22:07.115 --> 00:22:07.895
B however.

00:22:08.764 --> 00:22:13.385
This is our go-to for contrast
indicating something unexpected or

00:22:13.445 --> 00:22:15.215
opposite to what was just stated.

00:22:15.425 --> 00:22:21.574
C. Therefore, this is for showing a result
or consequence, like consequently not

00:22:21.574 --> 00:22:25.415
fitting D because this indicates a cause.

00:22:25.715 --> 00:22:29.189
She found questions challenging
because she studied diligently.

00:22:29.685 --> 00:22:30.465
No way.

00:22:30.915 --> 00:22:36.375
Step three, choose the best fit,
however, is the most suitable connector.

00:22:36.705 --> 00:22:40.605
It perfectly highlights the
contrast between her diligent study

00:22:40.815 --> 00:22:45.435
and the unexpected difficulty of
some questions combined sentence.

00:22:45.765 --> 00:22:50.025
She studied diligently for the
exam, however, she still found

00:22:50.025 --> 00:22:51.585
some questions, challenging.

00:22:51.915 --> 00:22:53.835
