00:23:01.370 --> 00:23:06.020
Which of the following connectors can be
used to combine the above two sentences

00:23:06.200 --> 00:23:09.560
into one options A, in contrast?

00:23:09.710 --> 00:23:11.180
B as a result?

00:23:11.390 --> 00:23:16.070
C. Furthermore, D, unless
understand the question before

00:23:16.070 --> 00:23:18.530
moving to explanation solution.

00:23:18.760 --> 00:23:22.810
Step one, understand the
relationship between the sentences.

00:23:23.260 --> 00:23:28.090
Sentence one describes the government
putting new policies into action.

00:23:28.449 --> 00:23:31.360
Sentence two describes
inflation going down.

00:23:31.810 --> 00:23:36.610
Common sense tells us that decline
in inflation is an outcome, a direct

00:23:36.610 --> 00:23:39.220
result of those new policies, right?

00:23:39.699 --> 00:23:43.419
We need a connector that shows
this cause and effect relationship,

00:23:43.629 --> 00:23:45.189
like pressing the doorbell.

00:23:45.490 --> 00:23:47.350
As a result, the bell rings.

00:23:47.680 --> 00:23:50.350
Step two, analyze the given options.

00:23:50.650 --> 00:23:54.100
A. In contrast, this is
for showing opposition or

00:23:54.100 --> 00:23:56.140
difference, not applicable here.

00:23:56.410 --> 00:23:59.260
B. As a result, this is perfect.

00:23:59.470 --> 00:24:04.240
It expresses consequence or outcome,
which is exactly what we identified.

00:24:04.505 --> 00:24:09.785
C. Furthermore, this just adds more
information, like, moreover, doesn't show

00:24:09.785 --> 00:24:13.655
cause D unless this expresses a condition.

00:24:13.835 --> 00:24:17.915
If not, for example, unless
you study, you won't pass.

00:24:18.095 --> 00:24:19.265
Not relevant here.

00:24:19.565 --> 00:24:23.135
Step three, choose the
best fit as a result.

00:24:23.315 --> 00:24:27.935
Accurately conveys that the decline in
inflation was a direct consequence of

00:24:27.935 --> 00:24:30.395
the government's new economic policies.

00:24:30.565 --> 00:24:35.185
Combined sentence, the government
implemented new economic policies.

00:24:35.455 --> 00:24:39.385
As a result, the began
